            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Can you use [`Session#next`](https://github.com/neovim/neovim-ruby/blob/25560e46e2d0027c8c6e4b000b16e9376d8253c5/lib/neovim/session.rb#L40) or [`Session#run`](https://github.com/neovim/neovim-ruby/blob/25560e46e2d0027c8c6e4b000b16e9376d8253c5/lib/neovim/session.rb#L30) ? The session is accessible as a reader on the client, i.e. `client.session`.",
